<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.9">
<l>kuṉṟāl māri paḻutākkik koṭiyē riṭaiyāḷ poruṭṭāka</l>
<l>vaṉṟāḷ viṭaiyē ḻaṉṟaṭartta vāṉōr perumāṉ māmāyaṉ</l>
<l>ceṉṟāṉ tūtu pañcavarkkāyt tirikāṟ cakaṭañ ciṉamaḻittu</l>
<l>kaṉṟāl viḷaṅkā yeṟintāṉūr kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram, the city of the one</l>
<l rend="indent">who threw at woodapples with a calf,</l>
<l>The great lord of celestials who once conquered seven strong-legged bulls</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of the one with a creeper-like waist,</l>
<l>Having made the downpour pointless with a mountain, great Māyaṉ</l>
<l>The one who went as a messenger for the Five,</l>
<l rend="indent">having destroyed the wrath of the rolling, wheeled cart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
